document: John Smith is the CEO of TechCorp. He became CEO in 2020.
Jane Doe founded TechCorp in 2010 and served as CEO until 2020.
TechCorp started as a small software development company in 2010 and has since expanded into various tech sectors including AI and cloud computing.
TechCloud, launched in 2015, is TechCorp's flagship cloud computing platform.
TechCorp's headquarters is located in San Francisco, California.
